---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About"
	description="ML Engineer transitioning to AI Safety Research Engineering."
	eyebrow="About"
>
	<!-- Intro -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">About</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-ink text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">ML Engineer with 7+ years of industry experience, pivoting to AI Safety research to work on one of the most important problems of our time.</p>
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">I assign high probability to transformative AI arriving soon. I'm sure it will be wild — and there are real alignment and societal risks on the horizon. I focus on making contributions that optimize for worlds where humans flourish in the long run and the transformation happens cleanly.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Research Focus -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Research Focus</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">Currently focused on AI Control — investigating multi-monitor ensemble techniques that enhance the safety-usefulness Pareto frontier. As a SPAR (Supervised Program for Alignment Research) Fellow, I've developed diverse monitor ensembles for detecting backdoored code, combining prompting and fine-tuning approaches.</p>
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">My work also spans mechanistic interpretability and LLM evaluation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Industry Background -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Industry Background</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">My engineering career spans fraud detection, identity verification, and ML infrastructure at companies including Capital One and Synapse Financial Technologies. I've led teams, shipped production ML systems processing millions of transactions, and built tooling that serves entire ML engineering organizations.</p>
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">This background gives me strong foundations in building reliable, scalable AI systems — skills directly transferable to safety research engineering.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Skills & Tools -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Skills & Tools</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Programming</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Python, C++, Bash, Linux, PyTorch, Keras, fastai, wandb, Scikit-learn, Pandas</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Infrastructure</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Git, Docker, Kubernetes, AWS, Hadoop, Spark, AirFlow, MongoDB, SQL, Redis</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">AI Safety</h3>
						<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Inspect AI, TransformerLens, SAELens, HuggingFace Transformers, Activation Steering, Linear Probing</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Certificates -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Certificates</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">AWS Certified Machine Learning — Specialty</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>Jul 2025</time></p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Full Stack Deep Learning Bootcamp</h3>
							<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Berkeley, CA</p>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>2019</time></p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Education -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Education</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Galvanize Data Science Immersive</h3>
							<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">San Francisco, CA — 700+ hours of hands-on training in Python, Statistics, ML, and Data Processing</p>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>2017</time></p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">B.S. in Finance, with Distinction</h3>
							<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Belarusian State Economic University</p>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>2010</time></p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
